# Contact form delivery (Web3Forms — https://web3forms.com)
#
# 1. Sign up at web3forms.com using ashishadhikari481@gmail.com
#    (messages are delivered to the inbox the key is registered under).
# 2. Copy your Access Key below.
# 3. For local dev: copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the value.
#    For production: add WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY in your Netlify site settings
#    (Site configuration → Environment variables), then redeploy.
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key
